title: GM warns Silicon Valley: Prepare to compete over driverless cars - Seattle Times
text:
That might as well have been the message Thursday from General Motors to Google, Apple and anyone else with designs on dominating the market for autonomous cars. The 107-year-old automaker told Wall Street analysts Thursday that it intends to lead no matter what form of transportation people pick in the future.
 Seattle Times.
